            section.grid.x12c#decisions
                h2.l-sect Design Decisions • Reflection
                h4.l-sect Procedural vs Compositional
                p.ml-sect A consistent critique that I received in the original iterations was addressing the seemingly arbitrary nature of our compositions. 
                    mark My redesign addresses this by using typography that emulates procedural patterns
                    |, reducing abstraction while reinforcing my art direction principle of layers of meaning.
