            section.grid.x12c#decisions 
                h4.l-sect Reframing Content Strategy • Reconsidering Purpose.
                p.ml-sect Beginning with a design-driven approach and then considering content strategy was difficult to frame meaningfully. I recognised a tendency in our team to force purpose and content onto the microsite, thus prompting a reframe &amp; redesign. It began with restarting research to find a framing opportunity, which came through Bords De Plateau. I then incorporated other feedback, and dived deep into our initial colour explorations, landing with my final deliverables.  

